# TypeScript in this repo

- Use explicit types for public route handlers and WS event payloads; reuse types from `src/ws/types.ts` and related modules when applicable.
- Avoid `any`; use `unknown` and narrow, or Zod-inferred types.
- Keep side effects (DB, IO) in services or dedicated modules, not scattered in route files beyond orchestration.
- Match existing import style (default vs named) in the file you edit.
